beloved husband of 65 years to irene.
loving father of debra (ronald) russell, gary (linda) andrus, and joyce (stan) savich.
dear grandfather of jeff & kevin, and chris, jessica & jeremy.
caring great-grandfather of 5. cherished brother of natalie (dick) beran.

family will receive friends in the tomon & sons funeral home, 7327 pearl rd.
